agreeable,
he
would
have
talked
to
Mrs.
Long.
But
I
can
guess
how
it
was;
everybody
says
that
he
is
eat
up
with
pride,
and
I
dare
say
he
had
heard
somehow
that
Mrs.
Long
does
not
keep
a
carriage,
and
had
