The
boy
protested
that
she
should
not;
she
continued
to
declare
that
she
would,
and
the
argument
ended
only
with
the
visit.
The
ladies
of
Longbourn
soon
waited
on
those
of
Netherfield.
The
visit
was
soon
returned
in
due
